CelcomDigi App – Built for you, around you
 
We are phasing out the MyDigi and Celcom Life apps by 31st December 2025. The CelcomDigi App is here to take their place, designed around what matters most to you: convenience, safety, and a little more delight every day.
 
Everyday tasks, made easy
* Everything in one app. Prepaid, postpaid, fibre, home wireless, even your family’s and supplementary lines, all managed in one place
* Check your internet usage at a glance
* View your full transaction history
* Pay bills in seconds
* Auto Reload Magic so you never run out of credit
* Pre-Book Roaming before you fly so you connect the moment you land
 
We take your safety seriously
* eKYC verification
* Linked device protection
* Biometric login and SSO
 
Everything else built in
* Stay entertained with Disney+ & more
* Travel smarter with roaming you set up in advance
* Keep your phone safe with the CD Safety Page, a dedicated hub with solutions and tips
 
Rewards you’ll love
* Vouchers, promos, and perks
 
For You – An app that understands your needs
* Smarter recommendations. From data passes to roaming deals, the app learns your habits and suggests what you’ll actually need
* Exclusive offers. Promos and bundles tailored to your lifestyle, not just generic deals
* Always relevant. The more you use the app, the more it adapts to bring you what matters most
 
Your daily dose of fun
* Daily Streak check-ins that unlock rewards
* 3-2-1 Weekly Surprise, every Wednesday at 3:21 PM
* Secret Surprise: Psst, Hidden freebies in the app
 
Something more
* Help That’s Always On with AI-powered support, instant answers any time of day
 
Why download?
With the CelcomDigi App, you can:
* Stay in control of usage, payments, and history
* Manage all your CelcomDigi services in one place
* Access entertainment, lifestyle, and protection services with ease
* Feel safe with security built into every layer
* Enjoy personalised offers and little surprises, every day
 
Download the CelcomDigi app and be ready for what’s coming soon!

MyDigital ID is an identity management and transaction signing platform. MyDigital ID is designed with the objectives to address vulnerabilities arising from various factors e.g. hostile applications on device, insecure communication channels and server-side storage of user credentials. 

MyDigital ID offers the following:
•	Strong security characteristic with a stringent 3-pass authentication mechanism for every transaction.
•	A convenient and secure way for third party applications to use the digital identity of mobile device users for authentication and digital signing.
•	Open ecosystem with systematic establishment of trustworthiness by users and mobile service providers

The most complete watching app is only on Vidio! From live sports and highlights, Vidio Original Series, to your favorite movies, dramas, and anime, everything is in one app. Enjoy exciting streaming anytime, anywhere!

· Vidio Originals – Enjoy exclusive shows of various genres like Bad Guys, Santri Pilihan Bunda 2, True Stalker, and Scandal 3: The Final & Sexiest.
· Korean Drama – Watch popular K-dramas like Love Scout, Motel California, The Queen Who Crowns, and Study Group.
· Top Movies & Drama – Watch the best movies and dramas, from Azzamine (Indonesian film), Flourished Peony (Mandarin drama), to Escape (Korean action film).
· Latest and Popular Anime – Watch your favorite anime like Solo Leveling Season 2: Arise from the Shadow and Naruto: Shippuden.
· TV Channels – Watch live national and international TV, starting from SCTV, Indosiar, tvN, Arirang, to Aljazeera.

Enjoy seamless HD streaming, subtitles in various languages, and ad-free viewing now!

To get the best experience, Vidio requires internet connection via WiFi or data package from your telecommunication provider (not included in Vidio subscription package). Internet quota consumption will determine by duration of content consumed.

Subscription via Vidio app
To subscribe, you can simply follow below easy steps:
1. Tap profile icon on the right corner
2. Tap Subscription
3. Select your preferred plan by tapping Activate
4. Sign in to your account (if you are not signed in). Vidio account is different from Apple ID
5. Tap Confirm button after entering your Apple ID password
6. Fill out any required payment information
7. Congratulations! Your Vidio account has been upgraded to Vidio Premier
 
If you are are subscribed using credit card, your subscription will automatically renew 24 hours prior to the end of each subscription period and will be charged through your iTunes account.
You can also cancel your Vidio Premier subscription anytime by managing your subscriptions "Manage Subscriptions" in the Apple Appstore. To cancel, please follow the instructions at https://support.apple.com/kb/ht4098. Cancellations in the middle of the active period will become effective as of the next billing cycle.There will be no refunds nor credit for partial subscription periods.
 
Terms of use - https://www.vidio.com/pages/premier-terms-and-conditions
Privacy Policy - https://www.vidio.com/pages/privacy-policy
For questions & feedback, please drop an email to info@vidio.com

Entertainment your way, stream anytime and anywhere with Vidio!

Sistem Skim Penstabilan Harga Minyak Masak (eCOSS) merupakan sistem pengurusan minyak masak paket bersubsidi 1kg yang dibangunkan oleh Kementerian Perdagangan Dalam Negeri dan Kos Sara Hidup (KPDN). 

Aplikasi mobil eCOSS merupakan sebahagian daripada sistem eCOSS yang berfungsi untuk merekodkan segala transaksi jualan minyak masak paket bersubsidi 1kg daripada pengilang, pembungkus, pemborong sehinggalah transaksi pembelian daripada pembeli di peringkat peruncit.

Say more with Threads — Instagram’s text-based conversation app.

Threads is where communities come together to discuss everything from the topics you care about today to what’ll be trending tomorrow. Whatever it is you’re interested in, you can follow and connect directly with your favorite creators and others who love the same things — or build a loyal following of your own to share your ideas, opinions and creativity with the world!

A few things you can do on Threads…

■ Access your Instagram followers
Your Instagram username and verification badge are reserved for you. Automatically follow the same accounts you follow on Instagram in a few taps, and discover new accounts too.

■ Share your point of view
Spin up a new thread to express what's on your mind. This is your space to be yourself, and you control who can reply.

■ Connect with friends and your favorite creators
Jump to the replies to get in on the action and react to commentary, humor and insight from the creators you know and love. Find your community and connect with people who care about whatever it is you’re interested in.

■ Control the conversation
Customize your settings and use controls to manage who can see your content, reply to your threads, or mention you. Accounts you’ve blocked will carry over from Instagram, and we’re enforcing the same Community Guidelines to help ensure everyone interacts safely and authentically. 

■ Find ideas and inspiration
From TV recommendations to career advice, get answers to your questions or learn something new from crowd-sourced conversations, thought leaders and industry experts.

■ Never miss a moment
Stay on top of the latest trends and live events. Whether it’s about new music, movie premieres, sports, games, TV shows, fashion, or the latest product releases, find discussions and receive notifications any time your favorite profiles start a new thread.

■ Leap into the fediverse
Threads is part of the fediverse, a global, open, social network of independent servers operated by third parties around the world. Servers share information with each other to enable people to connect and discover new things across the fediverse.

Aplikasi mobile myJPJ adalah gerbang yang menghimpunkan perkhidmatan untuk orang awam serta kakitangan JPJ. Orang awam boleh membuat semakan maklumat berkaitan perkhidmatan JPJ seperti saman, tarikh luput Lesen Kenderaan Motor (LKM),tarikh luput lesen memandu, nombor plat terkini dan lain-lain. Orang awam juga boleh mendaftar ID Awam dan membuat carian lokasi pejabat cawangan JPJ. Selain itu, terdapat pautan pantas ke aplikasi lain JPJ seperti JPJeBid dan JPJeQ. Log masuk sebagai Kakitangan JPJ mempunyai modul tambahan dan capaian pantas ke aplikasi eHadir.

The MyJPJ mobile application is a gateway that brings together services for the public and JPJ staff. The public can check information related to JPJ services such as summons, Motor Vehicle License (LKM) expiry date, driver's license expiry date, latest license plate number, and others. The public can also register a JPJeID and search for the location of the JPJ branch office. Additionally, there are quick links to other JPJ apps such as JPJeBid and JPJeQ. Logging in as JPJ Staff has additional modules and quick access to the eHadir application.

WE PRICE MATCH ► We aim to offer you the best possible price. If you find a cheaper option elsewhere, we'll refund the difference.
 
VERIFIED USER REVIEWS ► We have over 30 million verified hotel reviews to help you make your decision.
 
HOTEL AND FLIGHT BUNDLE BOOKING ► Save money by booking your hotel and flight together. If your flight is rescheduled, we'll guarantee your hotel room.
 
AND MORE.
 
TRIP.BEST RANKINGS ► You can find top attractions, family-friendly spots, natural sites and much more!
 
TRIP MANAGEMENT IN ONE APP ► You can add itinerary to your calendar, or save as a photo for offline use.
 
CAR RENTAL ► Free cancellation available!
 
Download the Trip.com app now to discover more amazing features and create your perfect trip - just like that!

• Use your camera to identify what you're looking at – whether that's a colourful butterfly, a spiky plant or anything else you're curious about.
• Translate over 100 languages on things like street signs, menus and any other words you can point your camera at.
• See something you like? Use your camera to find out where you can buy it.
• Refine your camera searches by adding words – whether you want those shoes but in 'blue', or want to learn how to 'repair' that broken piece on your bicycle.
• Search by singing, even when you've forgotten the lyrics. Hum a song into the Google app to find out what it is.
• Use your camera for homework help. With step-by-step guides and videos, you can learn ways to solve maths, chemistry, biology and physics problems.


Get personalised updates in Discover:
• Stay in the know about topics that interest you.
• Start your morning with weather and top news.
• Get real-time updates on sports, films and events.
• Know as soon as your favourite artists drop new albums.
• Get stories about your interests and hobbies.
• Follow interesting topics, straight from Search results.


Search safely and securely:
• All searches in the Google app are protected by encrypting the connection between your device and Google.
• Privacy controls are easy to find and use. Tap your profile picture to access your menu and delete recent search history from your account with one click.
• Search takes a proactive approach to filtering webspam to help ensure that you see safe, high-quality results.


More ways to access Google:
• Google Search widget — search from your home screen or lock screen with the new Google widget. Choose from two widgets, giving you a quick access search bar in both sizes, and other search shortcuts to choose from such as Lens, Voice and Incognito in the medium-sized widget.


Learn more about what the Google app can do for you: http://www.google.com/search/about

Privacy policy: https://www.google.com/policies/privacy

MyKasih App is created for the recipients of the Welfare Programme under the MyKasih Foundation. It's a quick and easy way for you to check your welfare programme wallet balance and expiry date, and quickly locate nearby merchants to make your purchase.
 
Key Features:
1. Check Merchant Location
Discover nearby merchants or enter a merchant name to search its location.
 
2. Item Category Reference List
Browse available products and locate their locations in the store.

3. Check Item Eligibility
Scan the item's barcode to find out whether the product is eligible under your programme.
 
4. Check the Welfare Programme Wallet Balance
You can now view your wallet balance easily within the app.

5. The MyKasih App consist of 2 languages - English / Malay.
